videos.description: Mississippi State's Jessika Carter gets the entry pass and flexes after she goes up and through the Texas A&M defense to score a difficult and-1 bucket in the paint.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Carter flexes on Texas A&M after battling for and-1 bucket) 2020/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter flexes on Texas A&M after battling for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Mississippi State's Rickea Jackson races down the court on the fast break and puts up a difficult layup through the Texas A&M defense to give the Bulldogs a 58-53 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jackson makes difficult fast break layup through contact) 2020/02/09 ESHEET
